        "annotations": {
          "note": "Prepare 4% PFA, DMEM/F12 prewarmed in a 37 °C water bath, PBS, 30% sucrose/PBS, OCT embedding solution, plastic molds, super frost glass slides, poly‑L‑lysine (PLL) and 1% sodium dodecyl sulfate."
